</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/2242287-kay">Kay</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s a reference to Muriel Spark&apos;s &quot;The Prime of Miss Jean Brodie&quot; where the teacher, Miss Brodie, has her own set of favourite girls. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's a reference to Muriel Spark's "The Prime of Miss Jean Brodie" where the teacher, Miss Brodie, has her own set of favourite girls. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
