<a href="/questions/1582323-did-anyone-else-hate-this-book-finding-it">Did anyone else hate this book, finding it really confusing? I read it to the end but the further I got the harder it was to know who the narrator was at any given time. A shame as I have read and loved other books by Joanne Harris</a>
