<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/9076262-jessica-nicastro">Jessica Nicastro</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Hi Sallie, I found that following the chess pieces helped to signify the narrator. There was a white king piece at the beginning of Straitley&apos;s chapte<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Hi Sallie, I found that following the chess pieces helped to signify the narrator. There was a white king piece at the beginning of Straitley's chapters and black pawns at the beginning of the unknown narrator’s parts (at least in my copy). <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
