          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/11490986-gentlemen-players">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1632609-anna?shelf=4-stars">4-stars</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1632609-anna?shelf=4-and-a-half-stars">4-and-a-half-stars</a>, 
