        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer79963031" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4536326661770003245">Excellent. Harris&apos;s best. Changing genres, yet keeping her mysterious twists and turns, G &amp; P will hold your interest. The characters are extraordinary,the plot paced just so, the story is superb. It is a clever tour de force. Nothing is as it seems.One of my top 5 books for 2006</span>
